A sociopolitical group under the auspices of People’s Choice, has described Sokoto State Governor Aminu Tambuwal as the best candidate the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) can field for the 2023 presidential election and the best choice for Nigeria. National coordinator of the group, Alhaji Muhammad Abubakar, who addressed journalists in Abuja, said Aminu Tambuwal, the Matawallen Sokoto and Sokoto state Governor, who has declared his intention to run for the highest political office, the Presidency, in Nigeria come 2023, is qualified for the presidential ticket of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). He said that Tambuwal has the capacity to be president because he has experience in the three arms of government and he is not only well prepared but also ready to fix the numerous problems of the country as President of Nigeria. “Tambuwal was not only a legislator, but also a lawyer by profession, meaning that he fits into the judiciary and at the same time, today he is a sitting governor serving his second term. “Tambuwal during his tenure as Speaker of the House of Representatives, made positive contributions at ensuring unity, integrity, peace and justice in the country. “Now as the governor of Sokoto state, he has also made giant strides in the areas of education, health, security, rural and urban development as well as youth and women empowerment,” he stated.